{"tid":1544472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日1930庶打集會無人講?","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T16:03:55.000Z","uid":178013,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"23c71c26cbf86b255d3bee52acf6ce09403cca68","tid":1544472,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔撚係呀嘛?<br />\n聽日1930「反濫捕 抗威權」集會無人講?<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>聽日星期五大家唔係掛住happy hour呀嘛?!<br />\n而家己經有過千名手足被捕<br />\n又有好多義士被班狗打到仆街<br />\n我地唔可以當佢地係condom!<br />\n我地一定要全力支援!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要盡力出動<br />\n因為今個星期如果人數一跌<br />\n就會令政府以為「徹回」收效<br />\n我地要大大力話俾政府知<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「五大訴求，缺一不可」唔只係口號<br />\n係香港人的共同願望，大家唔會退縮！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日1930庶打見!</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zsnDGH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zsnDGH.jpg&h=7ccc7ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日程:<br />\n6/9 1930「反濫捕 抗威權」集會<br />\n7/9 1300 「和你飛」3.0<br />\n8/9 1400  美國領事館"},{"pid":"81aebb6b024cf7c86458652b54b8bc3ba803e830","tid":1544472,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:39:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41c292e79a3b988a8df2d64b4d1cf85e8cfd07cb","tid":1544472,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"6/9 1930「反濫捕 抗威權」集會<br />\n7/9 1300 「和你飛」3.0<br />\n8/9 1400 美國領事館"},{"pid":"16a726b4daa8aa6829591d6bfc7b42a7fc31b04a","tid":1544472,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"6/9 1930「反濫捕 抗威權」集會<br />\n7/9 1300 「和你飛」3.0<br />\n8/9 1400 美國領事館"},{"pid":"3d6ae5c7d78fe524cf04a229aaa11c3833ed71cb","tid":1544472,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"聽日1930庶打見"},{"pid":"0