AXjTX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CAXjTX.jpg&h=00eeedf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，九月八日見</span>"},{"pid":"a999b835b5c83f64b62ee71c3067159665f078f2","tid":1544472,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"同學, 呢個係庶務個庶..."},{"pid":"f01f7130b45c969dec253312e46ae9dfc01328c3","tid":1544472,"uid":72916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"聽日我要見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdb22570ef045f7a75561ea1b987c411afeb5b5","tid":1544472,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:41:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWCvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=3ade788b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"bdd96c63c314f994732b1fb2f9d9429ba7e1b450","tid":1544472,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可 907機場一日遊 908美國領事館 <br />\n<br />\n<code>907機場 908美國領事館 831黑警恐襲 721元朗恐怖襲擊 811黑警還眼     #星火： 98190979 #民陣: 65499452 我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要去醫院驗傷  我唔會解鎖電話 我唔會簽任何文件</code>"},{"pid":"6d9cd9f4b3c72d1bb04a31c04e126bcb76279df3","tid":1544472,"uid"